---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Senior Marketing Manager | Jon Basildon";
---
<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="gif">
        <img width="300" height="259" alt="RaccoonSpaceGif" src="/space.webp"/>
    </div>
    <h1>
        Jon Basildon
    </h1>
    <small>
        Marketing Manager at Tesco
    </small>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
        Hello there! I'm a seasoned marketing manager with a passion for crafting compelling brand narratives and driving business growth. With over a decade of expertise in the dynamic world of marketing, I've had the privilege of shaping impactful strategies for renowned companies, including Tesco. My journey has equipped me with a deep understanding of consumer behavior and market trends, enabling me to devise innovative campaigns that resonate with audiences.
    </p>

    <p>
        I thrive on the challenge of creating engaging marketing initiatives that leave a lasting impression. My approach combines creativity with data-driven insights, ensuring measurable results and client satisfaction. Join me on this exciting venture, where we can transform ideas into powerful marketing solutions and make a significant impact in the digital landscape. Let's collaborate and elevate your brand to new heights!
    </p>

</Layout>
<style>
    /* small */
    small {
        background-color: #584966;
        color: #fdebf3;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-family: 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.3em 0.6em 0.2em;
    }

    /* Button */
    button {
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0);
        border: 2px solid #78c2ad;
        border-radius: 8px;
        color: #fdebf3;
        font: 600 16px 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        transition: background-color 0.4s, color 0.4s;
    }

    button:hover {
        background-color: #78c2ad;
        color: #1e1e2e;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .button {
        text-align: center;
    }

    /* Skill images */
    .link-images img {
        margin: 16px 4px;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .link-images img {
            height: 30px;
            width: 30px;
            margin: 16px 1px;
        }
    }
</style>
